with the local paper...

05:50.650 --> 05:52.173
where i was quoted as saying

05:52.208 --> 05:54.814
Ritalin was a godsend
when it came to test taking.

05:54.849 --> 05:57.159
And that sparked a whole debate
in the comments section--

05:57.194 --> 05:58.527
Is it ethical, is it not--

05:58.562 --> 05:59.974
And the boston papers
picked it up,

06:00.009 --> 06:02.670
And suddenly i'm in the middle
of this controversy

06:02.705 --> 06:04.134
That harvard wants no part of,

06:04.169 --> 06:06.410
So they rescind
my offer of admission.

06:07.254 --> 06:09.685
Well, i believe taking
a controlled substance

06:09.720 --> 06:11.757
