actually is illegal.

06:11.792 --> 06:13.341
No, it's a study aid,

06:13.376 --> 06:15.866
Just one step above
potent coffee.

06:17.357 --> 06:19.088
So what would you
like us to do?

06:20.408 --> 06:22.703
Get me reinstated
at harvard.

06:23.199 --> 06:24.990
I didn't do anything
to deserve this.

06:25.025 --> 06:26.311
I mean,
they're singling me out,

06:26.346 --> 06:27.779
And now
no school will take me.

06:27.814 --> 06:30.386
Where are your parents
with all this?

06:30.421 --> 06:32.441
Beyond devastated.

06:33.005 --> 06:35.777
It was their dream to see
their little girl go to harvard.

06:39.092 --> 06:40.935
I have to fix this.

06:40.970 --> 06:43.287
I screwed it up...

06:44.119 --> 06:47.421
and i have to fix this.

06:54.956 --> 06:56.828
What are you doing
at my desk?

06:57.043 --> 06:59.847
Oh. Oh. I-I was just
straightening up.

07:00.226 --> 07:01.942
That's what assistants do.

07:01.977 --> 07:03.607
You're not my assistant.

07:03.642 --> 07:04.666
Yes, i am, dear.

07:04.701 --> 07:08.080
No, i have an as--
Where is she?

07:08.115 --> 07:09.775
-Oh, francine?
-Mm.

07:09.810 --> 07:11.250
-I fired her.
-You--

07:11.285 --> 07:13.873
Too pretty, too young--
She's a distraction.

07:13.908 --> 07:15.192
All right,
i'm calling security.

07:15.227 --> 07:17.702
Look, honey, you sure
you want to make trouble

07:17.737 --> 07:19.228
For shirley's sister?

07:19.263 --> 07:21.309
-I mean, after all--
-Your name is catherine piper.

07:21.344 --> 07:24.976
You were fired for, among
other things, being psychotic.

07:25.011 --> 07:27.412
I also have cancer, dear.

07:31.157 --> 07:33.331
There. It's out.

07:33.510 --> 07:36.120
I am desperate
for a distraction,

07:36.155 --> 07:39.002
Anything to occupy myself
while...

07:39.543 --> 07:43.265
I'm sorry. I didn't come here
to indulge...

07:43.300 --> 07:44.928
you have cancer?

07:45.107 --> 07:47.581
Not really, but i could
get some if you'd like.

07:47.616 --> 07:49.391
Oh, 9-1-1.

07:49.426 --> 07:52.346
Look, if i could just
work here on a temporary--

07:53.406 --> 07:55.029
Oh, sorry.
